<section class="pg-section" data-section="Signature Facials">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Signature Facials</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Choose from our five specialized facial treatments, each designed to target specific skin concerns and deliver immediate, visible results. Click to learn more.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/a2e5efb60e6b.jpeg" alt="dermaplaning.jpeg" width="376" height="440" loading="lazy" />
