  <p class="pg-text">Book a Consultation! - Get 30 minutes with the esthetician for FREE or 30 minutes with Dr. Menon for $50 (applied towards treatment!)</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/consultation">Book a Consultation</a>
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="Find The Perfect Facial For Your Skin Goals">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Find The Perfect Facial For Your Skin Goals</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Tired of facials that promise amazing results but leave you disappointed?</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Most spas operate without any medical oversight or expertise. Their estheticians use basic products with no real understanding of skin science.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">At Menon Medispa, every treatment is backed by medical expertise. Under the guidance of board-certified physician Dr. Aditi Menon, our expert estheticians use medical-grade products and scientifically-proven techniques.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">This medical foundation means every facial is designed with a deeper understanding of how skin actually works, delivering visible improvements you can see after just one treatment.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Whether you're dealing with fine lines, stubborn dark spots, puffy skin, or want that healthy glow that photographs beautifully, our medically-informed approach gives you results that typical day spas simply can't match.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Don't just take our word for it...</p>
</section>

